{"tid":117313,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人發覺身邊好多人答非所問","createTime":"2017-02-12T06:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T10:20:41.000Z","uid":2663,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4a3ad4304c66d5267cff86c006f91c245259f3e","tid":117313,"uid":2663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:23:56.000Z","msg":"例如你老細問你份野比得佢未<br />\n你答佢5點半有<br />\n雖然都答到個答案<br />\n但呢條問題個答案應該係得/未得<br />\n你地又係點答?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟問題答果類人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 答到咪得果類人"},{"pid":"5ffd89d88b5f4e4978da5aa0e8ac826224831fbc","tid":117313,"uid":45920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:35:13.000Z","msg":"琴日食咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29caa7e8db8b0d2b8abfdd8e2bc607abf405c92e","tid":117313,"uid":77730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:40:11.000Z","msg":"直接答未得好唔俾面囉<br />\n答五點半比到 有一種雖然未得但我已經做緊既感覺"},{"pid":"7dbc339afe8fde254fb0388a50ecb67f6ae540fa","tid":117313,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:41:38.000Z","msg":"咁都叫答非所問?"},{"pid":"76fec7203af96583cafeb7546a09b825984f3e81","tid":117313,"uid":34196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:42:27.000Z","msg":"哦 呢啲嘢好死架啫"},{"pid":"61bf90a39360eb71e113a919c78f4cba164e97ee","tid":117313,"uid":2663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:45:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都叫答非所問?</blockquote><br />\n其實我解釋得唔好<br />\n應該分直接答同間接答<br />\n直接答係會中point啲，但一嚟好似樓上咁講會有啲唔禮貌，但肯定比到一個佢想知嘅答案<br />\n間接答人哋未必可以Get到個point,但就會知道更多其他以外嘅資訊"},{"pid":"aff4038863e3dded13cc2b609610978f5420da39","tid":117313,"uid":738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:53:22.000Z","msg":"佢答你差唔多就真係叫答非所問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacde786ba40c9